1
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:16,310
(Prefect Liu's wife)

2
00:00:16,440 --> 00:00:17,910
(is from Nanzhao?)

3
00:00:18,600 --> 00:00:20,349
(The person behind the poison camp)

4
00:00:20,760 --> 00:00:21,790
(she managed)

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:23,829
(was as His Highness
and I have guessed,)

6
00:00:24,239 --> 00:00:25,549
(it is indeed You Chen'an.)

7
00:00:29,199 --> 00:00:30,869
(When I met You Chen'an again,)

8
00:00:31,400 --> 00:00:33,110
(I couldn't help
but kill him immediately.)

9
00:00:33,640 --> 00:00:34,949
(He harmed my brother)

10
00:00:35,500 --> 00:00:38,090
(and raised poisonous worms
using the bodies of innocent people.)

11
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:39,798
(When You Chen'an removed)

12
00:00:39,799 --> 00:00:41,629
(his pitiful and innocent mask,)

13
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:43,629
(he was no different)

14
00:00:44,039 --> 00:00:45,520
(from a demon in the depths of hell.)

15
00:00:57,800 --> 00:01:03,070
♪Embark on a farewell
without saying goodbye♪

16
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:07,830
♪Build a bridge between life and death♪

17
00:01:08,040 --> 00:01:12,110
♪Hear a voiceless declaration♪

18
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:17,310
♪Break disguises, cross illusions♪

19
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:20,079
♪A fleeting life and delusions♪

20
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:22,919
♪The surface always conceals♪

21
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:28,110
♪Separate cause and effect♪

22
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:30,839
♪A twisted path, rising and falling♪

23
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:33,479
♪Seek the path amid the hazy unknown♪

24
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:38,319
♪Writing oblivion with a sharp blade♪

25
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:43,350
♪No matter how far, I gaze at the light♪

26
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:48,910
♪Fearing no wild lands, I press on♪

27
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:54,390
♪To see the tides of the world
once more♪

28
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:59,670
♪The deeper truth is buried, it grows♪

29
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:02,030
♪Until it is set free♪

30
00:02:11,040 --> 00:02:16,479
=The Imperial Coroner S2=
(Adapted from Idle Girl's The Constable's Wife)

31
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:19,559
(This story is entirely fictional.)

32
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:22,390
=Episode 25=

33
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:24,990
I said it long ago.

34
00:02:25,599 --> 00:02:26,830
Chu Chu is smart.

35
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:28,990
Not easy to deceive.

36
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,029
That's right,
Commandery Princess Consort An.

37
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:34,430
Your people will not make it here.

38
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,950
Our surprise force

39
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:38,749
will be here soon.

40
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:41,550
Is this how you treat our guests?

41
00:02:41,810 --> 00:02:43,830
Don't make yourselves
a laughingstock before her.

42
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,469
All of you, lower your blades.

43
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,629
General.

44
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:11,349
The forest is so quiet
that something feels off about it.

45
00:03:12,479 --> 00:03:13,110
Stop.

46
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,510
I haven't served you tea
after we've talked so much.

47
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:39,629
Forgive me.

48
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:41,909
This is our fault.

49
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:45,510
However, you can follow me
to Nanzhao Palace in the future.

50
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:47,349
I will treat all of you well.

51
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:49,550
How dare you invite us
to Nanzhao Palace,

52
00:03:49,639 --> 00:03:50,789
a den of treachery?

53
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,598
The result hasn't been decided yet.

54
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:53,749
God is fair

55
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:55,869
and won't stand with the beasts.

56
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:58,589
Chief Luo, you're so funny.

57
00:03:58,719 --> 00:04:00,110
At this point in time...

58
00:04:02,220 --> 00:04:04,959
(Windchime Message, Annan Army
broke the poisonous bugs' defense)

59
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,869
What's wrong?

60
00:04:06,310 --> 00:04:08,190
They broke
the poisonous bugs' defensive line?

61
00:04:11,759 --> 00:04:12,589
Jinli,

62
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:16,229
you might be ambushed
by poisonous bugs in this campaign.

63
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,950
Over the last few days,

64
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:21,669
through examining dead bodies
killed by these poisonous bugs

65
00:04:22,399 --> 00:04:24,310
and the eggs left on the dead bodies,

66
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,190
I made a powder.

67
00:04:27,079 --> 00:04:28,589
It might not kill the bugs

68
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,150
but it repels them.

69
00:04:32,519 --> 00:04:35,750
Brothers, scatter the powder
made by Commandery Princess Consort An.

70
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:25,710
What do you want?

71
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,109
Don't be afraid.

72
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,039
I'm here to save you.

73
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:30,229
All of this is thanks to Madam Yulan.

74
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,950
What do you mean, Your Highness?

75
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:36,318
Are you trying
to frame me with your words?

76
00:05:36,319 --> 00:05:37,669
I did not frame you.

77
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,239
We did find this place

78
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,270
because of you.

79
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,109
Save your energy.

80
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,989
It's no use
trying to sow discord between us.

81
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:49,549
I can betray anyone in the world

82
00:05:49,838 --> 00:05:51,589
except for His Highness.

83
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:55,150
I was simply saying

84
00:05:55,839 --> 00:05:56,950
but you became anxious.

85
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,630
It seems like

86
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,630
you care a lot about Second Prince.

87
00:06:05,279 --> 00:06:07,630
I heard Your Highness is a good coroner

88
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:09,070
but you know nothing else.

89
00:06:10,319 --> 00:06:11,630
In my opinion,

90
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:13,950
Your Highness's wisdom

91
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:16,510
surpasses that
of many others in the world.

92
00:06:17,199 --> 00:06:18,270
Next,

93
00:06:18,959 --> 00:06:22,119
is Your Highness
going to persuade us to surrender?

94
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:24,870
Whether you surrender or not,
it'll end the same.

95
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,310
Commandery Princess Consort An

96
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:31,830
is pure-hearted.

97
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:35,999
His Highness is indeed right.

98
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,080
I can't accept the praise.

99
00:06:37,439 --> 00:06:38,870
Those who are pure-hearted

100
00:06:39,839 --> 00:06:41,909
have already become your victims.

101
00:06:42,460 --> 00:06:45,770
(Windchime Message
The prison guards have been wiped out)

102
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:55,229
Kill them!

103
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:20,750
Tietou!

104
00:07:28,519 --> 00:07:30,150
Tietou, are you all right?

105
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,750
Your Highness!

106
00:07:48,879 --> 00:07:49,830
Attack!

107
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:16,638
Are you all right?

108
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:17,310
I'm fine.

109
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:19,070
They are running away.
Let's go after them.

110
00:08:27,199 --> 00:08:27,789
Your Highness,

111
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,589
go.

112
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:29,669
Hurry.

113
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,260
Be careful of the poisonous bugs.

114
00:08:46,279 --> 00:08:47,470
It's all thanks to your powder.

115
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:50,949
Let's go.

116
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,758
The tunnel
has been destroyed by the blast.

117
00:09:11,759 --> 00:09:13,100
It seems like they are prepared.

118
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,669
Thankfully, you arrive in time.

119
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:16,490
Otherwise,
they would've taken Chu Chu away.

120
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,110
This tunnel

121
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:22,750
should be connected
to this mountainside.

122
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,110
You Chen'an,

123
00:09:55,799 --> 00:09:56,750
we meet again.

124
00:09:57,020 --> 00:09:58,909
It has been a long time,
Commandery Prince An.

125
00:10:00,039 --> 00:10:02,870
I'm sorry for making you come all the way

126
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,398
to this desolated place.

127
00:10:04,399 --> 00:10:06,069
After you left hurriedly
at Weiguo Temple,

128
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,230
I knew

129
00:10:07,639 --> 00:10:09,789
we would meet one day again.

130
00:10:15,042 --> 00:10:16,983
Since you are now
in Jiaozhou's territory,

131
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,750
please come back with me

132
00:10:18,879 --> 00:10:20,230
and host Second Prince together,

133
00:10:20,799 --> 00:10:22,429
Madam Yulan.

134
00:10:24,799 --> 00:10:25,678
Commandery Prince An,

135
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:27,789
it seems like
you've investigated my background.

136
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,270
You are quick.

137
00:10:29,759 --> 00:10:32,150
You hid your identity
in Jiaozhou for more than a decade.

138
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,029
Finding out now

139
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,189
is still too late.

140
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:37,870
Come with us.

141
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:40,870
Let's not go to the Prefect's Residence.

142
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:42,780
I've been sick
of staying there all these years.

143
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:45,230
Commandery Prince An,
why don't you come with me?

144
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:48,549
His Highness and I
will host you together.

145
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,789
Host me?

146
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,909
Your Highness, you sent
Annan Great General

147
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,829
and the group of bandits

148
00:10:55,919 --> 00:10:57,549
to the mountain god temple

149
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:58,878
and only led

150
00:10:58,879 --> 00:11:00,870
a few of your soldiers to stop me.

151
00:11:01,559 --> 00:11:03,570
It seems like
you are very confident in your plan,

152
00:11:03,639 --> 00:11:04,709
Your Highness.

153
00:11:13,290 --> 00:11:14,309
Everyone, don't be afraid.

154
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,630
All of you are safe now.

155
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:23,069
Don't be afraid, it's all right.

156
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,110
Come.

157
00:11:24,279 --> 00:11:25,350
Have a drink.

158
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:31,789
There are more...

159
00:11:31,799 --> 00:11:32,750
What is it?

160
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,750
Speak slowly.

161
00:11:35,159 --> 00:11:39,029
They have a group of men with weapons...

162
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:52,310
General, all the poisonous bugs
have been exterminated.

163
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:53,990
Keep checking
to eliminate further risks.

164
00:11:54,159 --> 00:11:54,750
Yes.

165
00:11:58,050 --> 00:11:59,260
If it's inconvenient for you,

166
00:11:59,279 --> 00:12:00,350
I can deal with

167
00:12:00,759 --> 00:12:02,069
these Nanzhao people.

168
00:12:02,380 --> 00:12:03,390
There are so many of them.

169
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:04,960
How are you planning to deal with them?

170
00:12:05,875 --> 00:12:07,866
Tie them up and let them work as slaves.

171
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:09,590
If I put them in prison,

172
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,918
I still need to feed them.

173
00:12:10,919 --> 00:12:12,110
Chief, that's too much trouble.

174
00:12:12,519 --> 00:12:13,270
However...

175
00:12:13,519 --> 00:12:14,750
Do you have another plan?

176
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:15,750
Jinli.

177
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:17,909
Jinli,

178
00:12:18,279 --> 00:12:19,158
the number is wrong.

179
00:12:19,159 --> 00:12:19,959
What number?

180
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,909
The number of patients
and the dead bodies

181
00:12:22,399 --> 00:12:23,789
don't match the number of beds.

182
00:12:23,919 --> 00:12:25,110
There are

183
00:12:26,159 --> 00:12:27,310
more than 20 people missing.

184
00:12:43,799 --> 00:12:44,510
Your Highness,

185
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:45,590
we rushed here all the way.

186
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,839
Besides these people,
we didn't notice any soldiers.

187
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:48,470
Good.

188
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,990
Commandery Prince An, don't you get it?

189
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:54,709
What you can find out
and what you can do

190
00:12:55,039 --> 00:12:56,350
from the medical books

191
00:12:56,679 --> 00:12:57,789
and drug compendiums

192
00:12:58,679 --> 00:13:00,510
were accurately
predicted by His Highness.

193
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:03,630
You've put all your chips at the temple.

194
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:07,150
How can you defend yourself
against His Highness' counterattack?

195
00:13:07,679 --> 00:13:10,630
Since Chu Chu examined Liu Shijiang,

196
00:13:10,890 --> 00:13:12,678
all of you knew
that the unspeakable crimes

197
00:13:12,679 --> 00:13:13,949
at the mountain god temple

198
00:13:14,519 --> 00:13:16,429
would soon be exposed.

199
00:13:16,879 --> 00:13:18,390
That was why you used it as bait

200
00:13:18,759 --> 00:13:19,909
to trap me.

201
00:13:20,879 --> 00:13:21,789
You are right.

202
00:13:22,879 --> 00:13:24,029
With you in my hand,

203
00:13:24,180 --> 00:13:26,309
Xiao Jinli will have no choice
but to show restraint.

204
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,630
Ask the palace to send more soldiers.

205
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,270
Then, we can invade Jiaozhou
without much effort.

206
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:34,110
Your Highness, your sacrifice

207
00:13:34,519 --> 00:13:37,029
has saved
many of Nanzhao soldiers' lives.

208
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,750
You are doing a good deed.

209
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:39,789
Unfortunately,

210
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:43,189
I believe a real good deed

211
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:45,110
is to arrest and punish the criminals.

212
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:48,669
Chief Clerk Han.

213
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:09,870
Chief Clerk Han,

214
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,590
you are here?

215
00:14:14,559 --> 00:14:16,278
I've worked closely

216
00:14:16,279 --> 00:14:17,709
with many of you.

217
00:14:18,879 --> 00:14:21,789
Liu Shijiang holds a high position
without doing his work.

218
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:24,510
The imperial court
also neglects Jiaozhou.

219
00:14:25,279 --> 00:14:27,079
I've seen all the grievances

220
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,429
you've suffered.

221
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:31,309
The King of Nanzhao
respects men of talent.

222
00:14:31,559 --> 00:14:33,079
Why not switch to our side

223
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:34,429
and arrest Xiao Jinyu

224
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:37,878
so you can rise to the top

225
00:14:37,879 --> 00:14:39,350
and live a lavish life

226
00:14:39,639 --> 00:14:41,110
in the Nanzhao royal palace?

227
00:14:41,519 --> 00:14:42,309
Enough.

228
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:44,500
Stop trying to fool us
with your pretty words.

229
00:14:44,919 --> 00:14:46,270
Aren't you the ones

230
00:14:46,279 --> 00:14:47,760
who caused the suffering of Jiaozhou?

231
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:50,029
You're offering us wealth and fame now,

232
00:14:50,180 --> 00:14:52,220
but once we're no longer useful,
we'll be killed.

233
00:14:52,759 --> 00:14:54,870
I've disappointed Heaven's grace.

234
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,590
When I arrest all of you,

235
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:58,190
I'm willing to accept my punishment.

236
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,630
That depends on

237
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,990
whether you can do this or not today.

238
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:03,350
Kill all of them!

239
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:05,350
If they die,

240
00:15:05,519 --> 00:15:07,029
I will give you the antidote.

241
00:15:07,039 --> 00:15:07,909
Everyone,

242
00:15:08,399 --> 00:15:09,750
don't be fooled by her anymore.

243
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:13,029
The physicians of the Great Tang
can treat all of you.

244
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:18,829
What a joke.

245
00:15:19,100 --> 00:15:21,510
You don't even know
what poison they've been afflicted with.

246
00:15:21,679 --> 00:15:23,230
How can you promise to treat them?

247
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:26,270
If you listen to him, you'll only die.

248
00:15:28,759 --> 00:15:29,669
Besides,

249
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:32,150
Commandery Prince An is benevolent.

250
00:15:33,039 --> 00:15:35,630
He will not harm all of you.

251
00:15:35,799 --> 00:15:36,549
Am I right?

252
00:15:39,279 --> 00:15:40,069
Everyone,

253
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:41,150
you hear that?

254
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,150
Kill them!

255
00:16:32,559 --> 00:16:33,390
You're here.

256
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:36,429
Did you catch You Chen'an?

257
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:41,390
He escaped.

258
00:16:45,039 --> 00:16:46,789
We will not lose to the likes of them.

259
00:16:52,799 --> 00:16:55,750
This is where they raised
the poisonous bugs.

260
00:16:57,639 --> 00:16:58,709
You are weak.

261
00:16:58,710 --> 00:17:00,638
There are many things
that need to be handled in Jiaozhou.

262
00:17:00,639 --> 00:17:01,870
You should go back first.

263
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:05,189
I want to stay here for a while longer.

264
00:17:05,599 --> 00:17:06,469
Perhaps

265
00:17:07,039 --> 00:17:08,310
I will find some new clues.

266
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,429
I'll accompany you.

267
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:14,870
Have you found anything here?

268
00:17:16,759 --> 00:17:17,630
That tunnel.

269
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:19,669
They escaped from there.

270
00:17:21,319 --> 00:17:23,189
We chased them to a door

271
00:17:23,559 --> 00:17:25,870
and many poisonous bugs came out.

272
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:28,070
Although we were prepared,

273
00:17:28,359 --> 00:17:29,790
we were still delayed.

274
00:17:30,319 --> 00:17:31,429
When we came in,

275
00:17:32,319 --> 00:17:33,790
they blasted the tunnel.

276
00:17:41,720 --> 00:17:42,429
That's not right.

277
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:48,030
If they chose
to escape from here in the beginning,

278
00:17:48,839 --> 00:17:50,949
They should have chosen a perfect place.

279
00:17:52,799 --> 00:17:54,070
There are too many variables

280
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:57,189
by choosing this place.

281
00:18:00,559 --> 00:18:03,189
Do you mean
the tunnel was their only choice

282
00:18:03,440 --> 00:18:05,310
once they were here at the temple?

283
00:18:05,839 --> 00:18:07,110
If something goes wrong,

284
00:18:07,359 --> 00:18:08,830
they'd be trapped here.

285
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:10,150
Yes.

286
00:18:10,559 --> 00:18:11,909
With You Chen'an's consideration,

287
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:13,350
I'm sure he had a reason

288
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:15,350
for making this arrangement.

289
00:18:24,599 --> 00:18:25,390
Be careful.

290
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:31,870
These are the shells
of the poisonous bugs.

291
00:18:32,519 --> 00:18:34,800
They are the same
as the ones inside Prefect Liu's body.

292
00:18:39,319 --> 00:18:40,269
I get it now.

293
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:45,189
They are prepared
for all-out destruction.

294
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:47,989
They kept many poisonous bugs here

295
00:18:48,170 --> 00:18:49,630
so they can release them at anytime.

296
00:18:50,279 --> 00:18:53,269
Then, the bugs will enter Jiaozhou
through the mountains.

297
00:18:53,839 --> 00:18:54,989
The people of Jiaozhou

298
00:18:55,119 --> 00:18:57,030
will also become
vessels to raise the bugs.

299
00:18:58,440 --> 00:18:59,310
Jiaozhou

300
00:18:59,839 --> 00:19:01,669
will become a city of poison.

301
00:19:15,519 --> 00:19:16,310
Look over there.

302
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:19,030
That's Jiaozhou.

303
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:21,350
Thankfully, we exterminated

304
00:19:21,759 --> 00:19:22,709
all the poisonous bugs.

305
00:19:24,359 --> 00:19:25,989
However, among these residences,

306
00:19:26,799 --> 00:19:28,150
a few of them

307
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:31,390
are waiting for the ones who were harmed

308
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:32,870
to come home.

309
00:19:35,839 --> 00:19:37,509
You Chen'an's crimes are too many

310
00:19:38,039 --> 00:19:39,310
to put on paper.

311
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:41,509
However, justice will prevail.

312
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:43,490
Good and evil will be repaid in time.

313
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:45,469
He did all kinds of evil deeds

314
00:19:45,839 --> 00:19:47,390
and sacrificed the lives of many.

315
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,429
Why did he do that?

316
00:19:51,079 --> 00:19:51,989
For power

317
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:53,790
and authority.

318
00:19:55,319 --> 00:19:56,630
He wants power?

319
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:59,390
Didn't he say he just wanted to survive?

320
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:00,838
The throne

321
00:20:00,839 --> 00:20:02,949
has always been built
on blood and dead bodies.

322
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:05,229
If he wants to survive,

323
00:20:06,559 --> 00:20:08,110
someone has to die.

324
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:11,030
I don't know all these.

325
00:20:12,519 --> 00:20:14,469
I just know that he is a murderer.

326
00:20:15,880 --> 00:20:17,229
But he is from Nanzhao.

327
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:19,709
We can neither arrest him

328
00:20:20,599 --> 00:20:22,350
nor punish these criminals

329
00:20:22,599 --> 00:20:24,749
with the law of Great Tang.

330
00:20:26,279 --> 00:20:27,709
Justice will prevail.

331
00:20:29,599 --> 00:20:31,590
When will justice come?

332
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:34,318
He obtained authority

333
00:20:34,319 --> 00:20:36,050
by sacrificing the lives
of innocent people.

334
00:20:36,759 --> 00:20:38,709
That is the weapon we can use
to counter him.

335
00:20:40,250 --> 00:20:42,390
Now, you are the only one
who can retrieve this weapon

336
00:20:42,759 --> 00:20:44,469
so all those who were harmed

337
00:20:45,071 --> 00:20:46,542
can protect this land

338
00:20:46,559 --> 00:20:47,949
and their family

339
00:20:49,319 --> 00:20:51,269
with their last breath.

340
00:20:52,039 --> 00:20:53,189
They need you.

341
00:20:54,680 --> 00:20:56,070
They will also stand by your side.

342
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:00,310
When we are together,

343
00:21:00,759 --> 00:21:02,590
Jiaozhou will survive against all odds

344
00:21:03,319 --> 00:21:04,429
and avert disaster.

345
00:21:16,359 --> 00:21:18,350
We'll arrive at the exit
in another hour.

346
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:20,390
When we exit, we'll arrive in Nanzhao.

347
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:26,150
Why don't we take a break here?

348
00:21:39,079 --> 00:21:39,830
Your Highness,

349
00:21:40,279 --> 00:21:41,429
both of you should leave

350
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:42,630
to escape any pursuers.

351
00:21:45,119 --> 00:21:46,030
If it weren't for you,

352
00:21:47,280 --> 00:21:48,550
there wouldn't be any pursuers.

353
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:52,269
Your Highness!

354
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:53,709
Your Highness...

355
00:21:58,440 --> 00:21:59,550
Your Highness!

356
00:22:05,119 --> 00:22:06,110
An, I am...

357
00:22:18,920 --> 00:22:19,509
Your Highness,

358
00:22:19,759 --> 00:22:21,479
we have no evidence to prove

359
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:23,030
that she leaked the news about the camp.

360
00:22:23,319 --> 00:22:26,030
It's difficult to explain
to His Majesty when we go back.

361
00:22:27,200 --> 00:22:29,090
She has to die
whether we have evidence or not.

362
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:31,350
Moreover, she serves Father.

363
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:33,210
It's better for her to be dead.

364
00:22:34,880 --> 00:22:35,630
Take her away.

365
00:22:40,240 --> 00:22:41,509
I was incompetent.

366
00:22:42,279 --> 00:22:43,310
Please punish me, Father.

367
00:22:46,160 --> 00:22:47,110
Yulan.

368
00:22:51,319 --> 00:22:52,469
What happened?

369
00:22:54,039 --> 00:22:54,749
Father,

370
00:22:56,039 --> 00:22:57,390
I kept reminding her,

371
00:22:58,240 --> 00:23:01,550
but Madam Yulan still underestimated
Commandery Prince An and his wife.

372
00:23:02,480 --> 00:23:03,630
They found a flaw

373
00:23:04,500 --> 00:23:06,390
and the mountain god temple
was also destroyed.

374
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:08,030
All of the remaining plans

375
00:23:09,680 --> 00:23:10,669
failed.

376
00:23:11,839 --> 00:23:13,429
How did she die?

377
00:23:16,440 --> 00:23:17,949
We were ambushed by Xiao Jinyu.

378
00:23:19,319 --> 00:23:20,469
The Tang Army was close.

379
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:22,630
We had no way to escape

380
00:23:23,799 --> 00:23:25,390
and hid in a cave.

381
00:23:26,119 --> 00:23:27,110
In the cave,

382
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:29,509
she...

383
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:32,390
She was crushed by a falling rock.

384
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:35,150
Crushed by a falling rock?

385
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:37,229
Yes.

386
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:45,790
Back then,

387
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:49,598
I asked Yulan to help you in secret

388
00:23:49,599 --> 00:23:52,150
and manage the temple for many years.

389
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:56,110
She was cautious.

390
00:23:58,279 --> 00:23:59,030
I am

391
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:01,790
going to ask you again.

392
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:04,269
How did she die?

393
00:24:06,559 --> 00:24:07,110
Father,

394
00:24:07,559 --> 00:24:08,830
please investigate clearly.

395
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:10,870
Everything I said

396
00:24:12,759 --> 00:24:13,830
is true.

397
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:20,429
Don't you always want to know

398
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:22,749
who your biological mother is?

399
00:24:25,319 --> 00:24:25,989
She

400
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:35,269
is your biological mother.

401
00:24:44,319 --> 00:24:45,269
Didn't you say

402
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:48,558
my biological mother was long dead?

403
00:24:48,559 --> 00:24:51,830
She asked me to say that to you.

404
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:04,590
Be careful, it's hot.

405
00:25:09,079 --> 00:25:10,989
I have a distant relative at Qianzhou.

406
00:25:11,359 --> 00:25:12,709
I told them

407
00:25:12,880 --> 00:25:14,469
to take care of you for a while.

408
00:25:15,039 --> 00:25:16,360
It might be a few years, perhaps.

409
00:25:16,759 --> 00:25:18,550
When I find a way to make a living,

410
00:25:19,839 --> 00:25:20,959
I will pick you up.

411
00:25:20,960 --> 00:25:23,509
Mother, I'm not leaving!

412
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:26,350
Mother, I'm not leaving!

413
00:25:27,119 --> 00:25:28,070
Listen to me.

414
00:25:29,039 --> 00:25:29,558
Let's go.

415
00:25:29,559 --> 00:25:30,550
Hurry.

416
00:25:30,799 --> 00:25:31,439
Go.

417
00:25:31,440 --> 00:25:32,870
Mother!

418
00:25:34,599 --> 00:25:36,310
Mother!

419
00:25:37,839 --> 00:25:40,189
Mother!

420
00:25:46,400 --> 00:25:49,390
The real reason
your mother sent you away

421
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:53,709
was that all the spies
I sent to Jiaozhou were killed.

422
00:25:53,839 --> 00:25:54,959
I urgently needed

423
00:25:54,960 --> 00:25:57,909
a spy who could
approach the prefect of Jiaozhou.

424
00:25:59,079 --> 00:26:00,479
Your mother

425
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:01,989
learned this news for some reason

426
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:05,030
and volunteered to go to Jiaozhou.

427
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:07,429
Her only request was...

428
00:26:09,000 --> 00:26:09,749
Your Majesty,

429
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,469
if Chen'an can stay by your side,

430
00:26:11,559 --> 00:26:12,189
I will

431
00:26:12,519 --> 00:26:13,949
lay down my life for you.

432
00:26:19,519 --> 00:26:20,429
Chen'an,

433
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:21,830
do you still remember?

434
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:24,310
When you first came to the palace,

435
00:26:25,279 --> 00:26:28,949
I'd give you a set of pajamas
every year on your birthday.

436
00:26:29,839 --> 00:26:31,509
Back then, did you think

437
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:33,030
I treated you badly

438
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:35,479
and gave you those clothes

439
00:26:35,480 --> 00:26:38,229
that were worse
than the seamstress of the palace?

440
00:26:43,759 --> 00:26:44,390
Those...

441
00:26:45,519 --> 00:26:46,669
Were those...

442
00:26:47,839 --> 00:26:49,150
She sewd

443
00:26:50,079 --> 00:26:52,909
those clothes for you.

444
00:26:53,759 --> 00:26:54,550
Back then,

445
00:26:55,799 --> 00:26:59,070
I'd send her
your measurements every year.

446
00:27:01,039 --> 00:27:02,070
Those were

447
00:27:02,720 --> 00:27:04,790
your birthday present she gave you.

448
00:27:09,839 --> 00:27:12,949
Yulan was loyal to the palace
when she was alive.

449
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:14,949
Even if she made mistakes,

450
00:27:15,039 --> 00:27:18,909
it's all cleared now that she's dead.
I won't seek to punish her.

451
00:27:20,079 --> 00:27:21,150
You will be in charge

452
00:27:21,720 --> 00:27:23,269
of your funeral.

453
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:26,429
I wonder

454
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:29,118
if Yulan regretted

455
00:27:29,119 --> 00:27:30,679
exchanging her life

456
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:32,949
for your current situation

457
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:36,070
before her death.

458
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:10,790
Mother.

459
00:28:13,119 --> 00:28:13,989
I can

460
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:16,310
betray anyone in the world

461
00:28:16,519 --> 00:28:18,350
except for His Highness.

462
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:21,150
Why didn't you tell me?

463
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:24,550
Mother.

464
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:26,790
An, I am...

465
00:28:27,000 --> 00:28:28,999
Why didn't you tell me?

466
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:31,390
Why did no one tell me?

467
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:13,390
Mother.

468
00:29:17,480 --> 00:29:18,469
I'm here to see you.

469
00:29:22,400 --> 00:29:24,990
You've endured so much and
carried heavy burdens all these years

470
00:29:27,240 --> 00:29:28,909
yet I knew nothing.

471
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:32,550
I was unfilial.

472
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:36,110
I know

473
00:29:37,640 --> 00:29:39,749
you did everything for me.

474
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:43,790
You hoped I could survive,

475
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:46,630
not be humiliated

476
00:29:47,839 --> 00:29:50,269
and one day raise my head in pride.

477
00:29:54,079 --> 00:29:54,870
(Don't worry.)

478
00:29:56,640 --> 00:29:58,949
(I won't let you down.)

479
00:30:01,039 --> 00:30:02,159
(When I officially)

480
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:03,949
(stand on top of the Nanzhao Palace,)

481
00:30:06,440 --> 00:30:08,830
(I will surely
put your name in the family tree.)

482
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:13,550
(I will)

483
00:30:14,319 --> 00:30:15,469
(never spare)

484
00:30:17,240 --> 00:30:18,509
(anyone)

485
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:21,429
(who hurt you before.)

486
00:30:34,100 --> 00:30:40,399
(Mount Zhenyuan Abode)

487
00:30:40,400 --> 00:30:42,590
I thanked you many times.

488
00:30:43,440 --> 00:30:45,150
Chief Luo, you've provided much help.

489
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:47,990
If you need anything in the future,

490
00:30:48,200 --> 00:30:49,590
I'll do everything I can

491
00:30:49,600 --> 00:30:50,760
and not refuse your request.

492
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:53,190
I still have work in the army

493
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:54,229
so I can't stay for long.

494
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:55,909
Then,

495
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:58,110
I'll leave now.

496
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:00,229
You're leaving just like that?

497
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:05,310
I knew it.

498
00:31:05,319 --> 00:31:07,590
This is what I get
for helping the government.

499
00:31:07,799 --> 00:31:09,229
They are all heartless

500
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:10,590
and I don't get paid.

501
00:31:12,119 --> 00:31:12,870
You are right.

502
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:13,870
I'm so forgetful.

503
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:15,300
The men of the abode stopped working

504
00:31:15,319 --> 00:31:17,390
and sacrificed their lives
for the sake of Jiaozhou.

505
00:31:17,559 --> 00:31:20,469
Don't worry.
There's compensation and a reward.

506
00:31:20,839 --> 00:31:21,469
I will

507
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:22,870
deliver them in the future.

508
00:31:23,039 --> 00:31:25,639
People in the underworld like us
don't need so much money.

509
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:26,150
Then...

510
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:27,469
What do you want?

511
00:31:27,470 --> 00:31:28,580
I will do my best to get it for you.

512
00:31:28,599 --> 00:31:29,509
Then,

513
00:31:30,720 --> 00:31:33,269
I need to think about it carefully.

514
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:34,830
Sure.

515
00:31:35,319 --> 00:31:36,450
When you know what you want,

516
00:31:36,759 --> 00:31:37,749
you can tell me anytime.

517
00:31:48,599 --> 00:31:49,350
What else?

518
00:31:49,720 --> 00:31:51,030
We are alone here

519
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:52,310
without a witness

520
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:55,350
what if you forget about it one day

521
00:31:55,500 --> 00:31:56,690
and try to break your promise?

522
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:57,909
What should I do?

523
00:31:58,559 --> 00:31:59,509
Then,

524
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:01,150
should I write you a note?

525
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:03,269
Even His Majesty's handwritten decree
can be faked.

526
00:32:03,799 --> 00:32:04,550
That doesn't count.

527
00:32:05,119 --> 00:32:05,909
That's...

528
00:32:07,039 --> 00:32:07,830
That's...

529
00:32:11,519 --> 00:32:12,550
Leave me a token.

530
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:14,590
A token?

531
00:32:16,559 --> 00:32:17,598
But I didn't

532
00:32:17,599 --> 00:32:19,469
bring any valuable items with me.

533
00:32:20,519 --> 00:32:22,558
What do you think
is valuable enough to be a token?

534
00:32:22,559 --> 00:32:23,550
Just take it.

535
00:32:23,940 --> 00:32:30,859
♪The moment you smile,
let me cherish it for good♪

536
00:32:30,860 --> 00:32:37,170
♪Because of you I care about my life♪

537
00:32:38,140 --> 00:32:41,339
♪I'm not old yet, I still love you♪

538
00:32:41,340 --> 00:32:45,330
♪At last I settle down for you♪

539
00:32:45,980 --> 00:32:52,210
♪I can rely on you all my life♪

540
00:32:52,380 --> 00:32:58,250
♪Hope we'll spend our lives sweetly♪

541
00:33:01,390 --> 00:33:03,669
Your Highness, General Xiao
has returned to the army camp.

542
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:05,429
He asked me to inform you

543
00:33:05,430 --> 00:33:07,390
that all the arrangements
have been taken care of.

544
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:09,520
Chief Luo has been
safely escorted back to the abode.

545
00:33:10,359 --> 00:33:11,590
He left so quickly.

546
00:33:11,690 --> 00:33:13,310
Did he have something to do in the camp?

547
00:33:14,519 --> 00:33:16,150
Perhaps

548
00:33:16,599 --> 00:33:17,709
he was looking shabby

549
00:33:18,519 --> 00:33:20,269
and it might affect his image.

550
00:33:20,319 --> 00:33:21,509
He looked shabby?

551
00:33:22,519 --> 00:33:23,790
It might affect his image?

552
00:33:25,079 --> 00:33:26,669
When General Xiao came back,

553
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:28,469
his belt was missing.

554
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:34,189
Go.

555
00:33:35,079 --> 00:33:35,550
Yes.

556
00:33:39,039 --> 00:33:40,269
His belt was missing.

557
00:33:45,559 --> 00:33:48,269
In the ninth month of the Jiachen year,

558
00:33:48,270 --> 00:33:49,719
The Nanzhao army and the Nanzhao Mob

559
00:33:49,720 --> 00:33:52,630
started a confrontation at my border.

560
00:33:53,119 --> 00:33:55,590
Commandery Princess Consort An
was accidentally involved in it.

561
00:33:56,319 --> 00:33:58,159
Annan Army's soldiers
stationed at Jiaozhou

562
00:33:58,160 --> 00:33:59,479
were worried about Her Highness's safety

563
00:33:59,480 --> 00:34:01,390
and were forced to deploy
to quell the unrest.

564
00:34:02,079 --> 00:34:03,269
The battle ends today,

565
00:34:03,519 --> 00:34:06,989
The dead bodies of Nanzhao people
and the Nanzhao people who were captured

566
00:34:07,240 --> 00:34:08,869
will be returned to Nanzhao?

567
00:34:09,079 --> 00:34:09,590
This...

568
00:34:10,119 --> 00:34:11,590
When did this happen?

569
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:15,070
The Nanzhao army
mentioned in the document

570
00:34:15,199 --> 00:34:17,789
was the soldiers you lost in Jiaozhou!

571
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:20,030
The mob

572
00:34:21,079 --> 00:34:24,070
was your people
at the mountain god temple!

573
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:28,869
Look.

574
00:34:29,719 --> 00:34:32,678
Look what the two of you have done.

575
00:34:32,679 --> 00:34:35,269
You kept giving them excuses.

576
00:34:37,719 --> 00:34:39,430
There's news from Chang'an.

577
00:34:41,119 --> 00:34:43,789
Gao Luoqian suffered a complete defeat.

578
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:45,869
He has been detained
and questioned for his crimes.

579
00:34:45,880 --> 00:34:47,150
That's not possible.

580
00:34:47,320 --> 00:34:48,470
Not possible?

581
00:34:48,639 --> 00:34:50,349
I want to ask you two how it happened!

582
00:34:51,000 --> 00:34:52,558
When you accepted the mission,

583
00:34:52,559 --> 00:34:54,359
all of you sounded confident

584
00:34:54,360 --> 00:34:57,349
and was afraid you'd get less credit.

585
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:58,590
Right now,

586
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:01,669
all of you tell me

587
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:02,799
that it's one failure

588
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:04,110
after another.

589
00:35:05,320 --> 00:35:07,590
It was a good situation for us at first.

590
00:35:08,559 --> 00:35:11,590
Great Tang was busy
dealing with the Northern lands,

591
00:35:11,679 --> 00:35:13,550
the officials of Chang'an
were in turmoil,

592
00:35:13,560 --> 00:35:15,359
the poisonous bugs
made the people scared,

593
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:16,709
and Jiaozhou could be taken.

594
00:35:17,719 --> 00:35:19,510
Nothing was supposed to go wrong.

595
00:35:21,599 --> 00:35:24,709
Why do I still need
the two of you alive?

596
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:26,550
Father,

597
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:30,869
I made more preparations
before I came back.

598
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:32,349
Father, please

599
00:35:32,599 --> 00:35:34,869
allow me to redeem myself
through the credit

600
00:35:35,639 --> 00:35:36,630
of capturing Jiaozhou.

601
00:35:38,079 --> 00:35:38,669
Father,

602
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:41,678
it's do-or-die.

603
00:35:41,679 --> 00:35:42,750
We can only take a gamble.

604
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:44,829
If we can capture Jiaozhou,

605
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:46,910
we'll have more bargaining chips

606
00:35:47,239 --> 00:35:48,829
when Great Tang's document arrives.

607
00:35:49,719 --> 00:35:50,510
Perhaps

608
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:53,430
it might even spare Lord Gao's life.

609
00:36:02,679 --> 00:36:03,430
You Longsheng.

610
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:04,269
Yes.

611
00:36:04,639 --> 00:36:05,590
You must

612
00:36:06,599 --> 00:36:09,229
work with your second brother on this.

613
00:36:09,679 --> 00:36:10,669
Nothing can go wrong.

614
00:36:10,670 --> 00:36:11,789
I'm going to work with him?

615
00:36:12,360 --> 00:36:13,389
I've made my decision.

616
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:14,950
Yes.

617
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,940
You Longsheng will
have the military authority.

618
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:18,749
You Chen'an will supervise the army

619
00:36:19,239 --> 00:36:21,189
and be in charge of Jiaozhou's battle.

620
00:36:22,559 --> 00:36:23,110
Yes.

621
00:36:25,760 --> 00:36:26,590
You may leave.

622
00:36:53,039 --> 00:36:53,749
Your Highness.

623
00:36:55,690 --> 00:36:56,749
How is it, Your Highness?

624
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,669
Has the King of Nanzhao agreed?

625
00:37:00,559 --> 00:37:02,269
Father wants us to work together.

626
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:05,709
Even so,

627
00:37:07,559 --> 00:37:09,269
You Longsheng has the military authority.

628
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:12,269
If Eldest Prince captures Jiaozhou,

629
00:37:13,320 --> 00:37:14,910
His power will be unstoppable.

630
00:37:15,119 --> 00:37:16,829
You won't receive any credit for it.

631
00:37:17,159 --> 00:37:17,829
Your Highness.

632
00:37:18,639 --> 00:37:20,470
When the time comes, it'll be dangerous.

633
00:37:22,199 --> 00:37:23,150
Once the battle begins,

634
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:28,229
my brother cannot
return to Nanzhao alive

635
00:37:31,119 --> 00:37:32,309
with credit.

636
00:37:35,159 --> 00:37:36,150
Let's prepare

637
00:37:37,199 --> 00:37:38,470
what we should.

638
00:37:40,719 --> 00:37:41,950
I'll get them ready now.

639
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:42,590
Also,

640
00:37:45,159 --> 00:37:46,110
no matter what,

641
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:49,229
thank you for helping me.

642
00:38:10,719 --> 00:38:12,718
Guo, you are amazing.

643
00:38:12,719 --> 00:38:14,359
Not only did you escape alive,

644
00:38:14,360 --> 00:38:15,950
but you even brought people to save us.

645
00:38:16,159 --> 00:38:17,189
That's nothing.

646
00:38:17,199 --> 00:38:19,829
I'm going to learn Kungfu from Chief Luo
in the future

647
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,470
and be in the escort business.

648
00:38:23,239 --> 00:38:24,829
Do we still have a future?

649
00:38:30,079 --> 00:38:31,590
I heard the soldier say

650
00:38:31,880 --> 00:38:33,229
this Princess Consort is amazing.

651
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:35,349
Can she really treat our illnesses?

652
00:38:36,760 --> 00:38:38,150
Don't say something so dejected.

653
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:40,759
Not dying at a filthy place
is already a good thing.

654
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:41,669
Look.

655
00:38:42,639 --> 00:38:44,829
This place is dirty and dangerous.

656
00:38:45,679 --> 00:38:47,709
Will the Princess Consort come here?

657
00:38:48,239 --> 00:38:49,189
Indeed.

658
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:55,550
Jiaozhou and Great Tang
have never abandoned all of you.

659
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:58,100
The state government
brought the best physician here.

660
00:38:58,119 --> 00:38:59,789
Even the city's physicians are here.

661
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:01,150
I might not be an expert,

662
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:02,309
but I've seen

663
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:04,709
my fair share of weird illnesses
in the capital.

664
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:06,309
I will do my best to treat all of you.

665
00:39:07,119 --> 00:39:07,919
Wonderful.

666
00:39:07,920 --> 00:39:08,709
Wonderful.

667
00:39:09,159 --> 00:39:10,470
Wonderful.

668
00:39:11,079 --> 00:39:12,349
If we work together,

669
00:39:12,599 --> 00:39:13,910
everything will be better.

670
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:14,990
So,

671
00:39:15,039 --> 00:39:16,309
please trust us

672
00:39:16,310 --> 00:39:17,580
and cooperate with the treatment.

673
00:39:17,599 --> 00:39:19,550
We mustn't surrender to Nanzhao.

674
00:39:19,920 --> 00:39:20,590
All right?

675
00:39:22,639 --> 00:39:24,829
Your Highness, we will never surrender.

676
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:25,430
Yes.

677
00:39:25,599 --> 00:39:26,558
We won't surrender.

678
00:39:26,559 --> 00:39:27,590
Yes.

679
00:39:27,600 --> 00:39:29,360
- We won't surrender.
- We won't surrender.

680
00:39:29,690 --> 00:39:30,550
We won't surrender...

681
00:39:31,679 --> 00:39:32,349
What's wrong?

682
00:39:33,800 --> 00:39:34,359
Hurry.

683
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:35,400
Send him to get treatment.

684
00:39:52,660 --> 00:39:55,700
♪Time drips away
like fading crimson scent♪

685
00:39:55,700 --> 00:39:59,220
♪The hardships of arrival pass
in a fleeting blink♪

686
00:39:59,580 --> 00:40:02,340
♪Palm lines carry
the footprints of memory♪

687
00:40:02,820 --> 00:40:06,300
♪Leading us out of every winding turn♪

688
00:40:07,140 --> 00:40:10,940
♪If two hearts can fly as one
then storms are part of the way♪

689
00:40:10,940 --> 00:40:14,220
♪Looking back the sky
has already cleared♪

690
00:40:14,340 --> 00:40:16,860
♪Your branches entwined with mine♪

691
00:40:16,860 --> 00:40:20,260
♪Bound together in mutual reliance♪

692
00:40:22,380 --> 00:40:25,460
♪Rugged roads become
the paths of sun and moon♪

693
00:40:25,460 --> 00:40:28,540
♪Fireflies like stars circle
through the seasons♪

694
00:40:29,380 --> 00:40:31,500
♪Shining with the hope of dreams♪

695
00:40:31,500 --> 00:40:36,180
♪This world is no longer in rags♪

696
00:40:36,900 --> 00:40:40,540
♪Only by holding you in my heart
do I dare embrace fear♪

697
00:40:40,540 --> 00:40:43,820
♪Quietly waiting for rumors to fade♪

698
00:40:44,220 --> 00:40:46,540
♪Together we face the tides of fate♪

699
00:40:46,540 --> 00:40:50,700
♪Turning the course of heaven and earth♪

700
00:40:50,820 --> 00:40:53,420
♪This love was never easy♪

701
00:40:53,420 --> 00:40:57,820
♪So life and death will not part us♪

702
00:40:58,180 --> 00:41:00,740
♪Like sinking into the deep sea♪

703
00:41:00,740 --> 00:41:05,740
♪The first breath upon awakening♪

704
00:41:05,740 --> 00:41:07,980
♪This bond will never waver♪

705
00:41:07,980 --> 00:41:12,860
♪So we stay together
till our hair turns white♪

706
00:41:12,860 --> 00:41:15,340
♪I ask time itself to hold the pen♪

707
00:41:15,340 --> 00:41:20,380
♪And write the ending of eternity♪

708
00:41:20,420 --> 00:41:22,700
♪This love was never easy♪

709
00:41:22,700 --> 00:41:26,860
♪So I believe without doubt♪

710
00:41:27,500 --> 00:41:30,100
♪Like a thousand sails passing by♪

711
00:41:30,100 --> 00:41:35,020
♪Reaching shore
at the first light of dawn♪

712
00:41:35,500 --> 00:41:37,380
♪This bond will never waver♪

713
00:41:37,380 --> 00:41:42,380
♪So joy and sorrow
are no longer ours to choose♪

714
00:41:42,380 --> 00:41:44,780
♪I will prove it
with the rest of my life♪

715
00:41:44,780 --> 00:41:50,540
♪Together at the edge
of the world without an end♪
